properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 15 at 3:30AM EST until January 17 at 7:00AM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 20 to 30 kt with gusts up to 40 kt and
seas 3 to 6 ft expected.

* WHERE...New Jersey and Delaware Atlantic Coastal waters out 20
nm.

* WHEN...From 7 AM Thursday to 7 AM EST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 7 AM THURSDAY TO 7 AM EST FRIDAY... ...DENSE FOG ADVISORY IS CANCELLED
